title: Definitions
context: [ยง185-1] Definitions. As used in this chapter, unless the context otherwise requires: &ldquo;Administrator&rdquo; means the administrator of forestry and wildlife. &ldquo;Board&rdquo; means the board of land and natural resources. &ldquo;Branch&rdquo; means an area comprising a county of the State. &ldquo;Department&rdquo; means the department of land and natural resources. &ldquo;Manager&rdquo; means the forestry and wildlife manager of a designated branch.
